# isIncoming()

**Instance Method**

Returns TRUE if the channel is an incoming channel.

## Declaration

```swift
func isIncoming() -> Bool
```

## Return Value

Returns TRUE if the channel is an incoming channel.

## Discussion

An incoming channel is one that was initiated by a remote device.
